external and internal rules to all our people and external third parties. The reports generated by these channels are forwarded to our Compliance organization and followed up. The same channels can also be used to report human rights violations to the company. COMPLIANCE AND ETHICS

Networks and coalitions We maintain a regular dialog with our peers, and we aim to

establish mutual trust and drive a more in-depth discussion on human rights. This kind of dialog focuses on discussing challenges and solutions, addressing areas of improvement with regard to responsible business conduct practices, and identifying potential areas to join forces. We firmly believe that we can achieve faster, more impactful progress through collective action compared to acting alone.